Package aas_core.aas3_0.types.model

Interface ICapability

All Superinterfaces:
IClass, IHasDataSpecification, IHasExtensions, IHasSemantics, IQualifiable, IReferable, ISubmodelElement
All Known Implementing Classes:
Capability, EnhancedCapability
public interface ICapability extends ISubmodelElement
A capability is the implementation-independent description of the potential of an asset to achieve a certain effect in the physical or virtual world.

The IHasSemantics.getSemanticId() of a capability is typically an ontology. Thus, reasoning on capabilities is enabled.
